{"type": "article", "id": 14544, "title": "栅栏桌椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-07T07:00:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141156EH9GF8jgzZ6WdIxJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组像栅栏一样的桌椅来自法国设计师 Ronan 、 Erwan Bouroullec 和丹麦家具品牌 Hay。它们用钢管打造，根据高矮宽窄和特定的弧线表示有不同的功能，极简统一。设计师想要它们适合任何环境，不分室内室外，公共或私人，并同时具备力量和优雅的特征。但其实它们看上去非常具有艺术感，尤其是在光线照射下投放的影子，和椅子一起呈现出孤独的感受，令人想起 Jasper Morrison 的 Thinking Man's Chair 。坐上去是否舒服反而是次要的了。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142029jwSypcrgbJAPZvBI.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"538\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.14957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142029X8dPmhJnpw2bVo4Z.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142029G2Exi7Y94OcLa5X3.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142030Ho0e5RKMbEid4DNa.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"734\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89731051\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}